        "Larian Studios Head Suggests Next Game May Come in 2029, but Maybe Not: ‘Don’t Hold Us to a Date’",
      link: "https://sea.ign.com/baldurs-gate-iii/221182/news/larian-studios-head-suggests-next-game-may-come-in-2029-but-maybe-not-dont-hold-us-to-a-date",
